longBusinessSummary: GameSquare Esports Inc. operates as a gaming and esports company in Canada. The company bridges the gap between global brands and the large gaming and esports communities. It also provides consulting, influencer marketing and promotion, broadcast talent management, and other services. In addition, the company intends to acquire assets and entities serving the gaming and esports markets. GameSquare Esports Inc. is based in Toronto, Canada.
